name: Invisible Button CSS
format:
<style>
    /* Disable the default Node-RED button styling */
    .invisible-button.nr-dashboard-button {
        background-color: transparent !important;
        border: none !important;
        box-shadow: none !important;
        color: inherit !important;
        text-shadow: none !important;
    }

    /* Make the button invisible */
    .invisible-button.nr-dashboard-button {
        opacity: 0;
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
    }
</style>
